@jacobandco x @alecmonopoly Astronomia 💰

To celebrate the unique partnership between Jacob & Co and Alec, the pair have launched this exclusive timepiece costing $600,000 and limited to 9 pieces.

The colourful animated watch has a black sky layer base housed in an 18K rose gold case with a curved sapphire crystal dome and four sapphire crystal windows on the side that provide a full view of the artistic and mechanical creations inside.

By: @jacobandco & @alecmonopoly

#jacobandco #watch #watches #watchcollector #watchesofinstagram #watchaddict #watchlover #alecmonopoly #artisanmade #millionairesurroundings

node.text:
Introducing the Astronomia Tourbillon Baguette Ruby Degrade Dial; by @jacobandco

We are thrilled to present to you another one of Jacob & Co’s incredible watches; this particular watch features the blue lacquered magnesium globe with the continent’s finished in rose gold to ensure the consistency in weight, as all four satellites have to weigh the same keeping the watch perfectly balanced.

Serving as a spectacular backdrop for the satellites turning above is the base dial completely invisibly-set with baguette-cut multi-color gemstones. This makes for a unique coming together of gem-cutting and gem-setting prowess and ultra-high-end watchmaking, as can only ever be experienced in a Jacob & Co creation.

By: @jacobandco | #millionairesurroundings #jacobandco

#watch #watchesofinstagram #luxurylifestyle #watchcollector #watchaddict #artisan #jewellery #jewelry #limitededition
